a bulletproof vest.

162
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,600
The bullet didn't cause
a fatal wound.

163
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:11,800
Ye Ying.

164
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,480
You've got the wrong person.

165
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:15,920
I'm not Ye Ying.

166
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,600
I'm An Ning.

